>\n<br />\n其他行業一樣"},{"pid":"50d1c691db8f46c8edd4f13eb086d5b1ad68dc4f","tid":1944672,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"冇所謂，呢輪冇乜好戲上"},{"pid":"6424b24cb8871aa93ea065e45b1ae934d3a281f1","tid":1944672,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"仲有好多嘢應該要停<br />\nGym Room<br />\n<br />\n食肆只供外賣<br />\n<br />\n巴士停企位（唔係話完全唔企得人，但一有人企就必須要停止上客）<br />\n大幅加密班次<br />\n同時私家車退還20%牌費<br />\n但限單雙號行車，以減低交通流量<br />\n星期日全面開放<br />\n（特別字母，將會領取單雙號，根據以上限制行車）<br />\n泊車轉乘<br />\n轉乘的那一程完全免費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將長者2蚊優惠限為一日4次，減少非必要跨區<br />\n<br />\n馬會投注轉為電子形式<br />\n<br />\n賽馬將轉為電視播放<br />\n但禁止公眾場合轉播<br />\n各位可以返屋企自己睇"},{"pid":"c15496e31bdcd0608efb556daa44165cf017060f","tid":1944672,"uid":24131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ac072f02d5e9c93ca6473d74a55cb0f835b2f20","tid":1944672,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n<br />\n唔禁巴士地鐵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"蘋果出左新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府要求封鋪係要賠錢 所以佢唔要求酒吧同餐廳封<br />\n因為要錢比所以餐廳<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，香港至今有逾450宗個案，為減少感染，酒吧冇酒供應，麥當勞和大家樂已停晚市堂食，《蘋果》收到消息，戲院商會明日會跟商經局開會，就政府要求院商停業14日事宜商討，好大機會由後日（28日）起停業，不過戲院商會就租金和補償跟政府商討。<br />\n<br />\nref:<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200326/4MPJPGDWU7LHAT2NBMFA2YJO5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200326%2F4MPJPGDWU7LHAT2NBMFA2YJO5A%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=2aa63d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200326%2F4MPJPGDWU7LHAT2NBMFA2YJO5A%2F&h=1fb06e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200326/4MPJPGDWU7LHAT2NBMFA2YJO5A/</a>"},{"pid":"e4103810ecf0d29945c06ce3456d